 2- (byk yạ yswʿ ạlmsyḥ .. qlby mlyạn bạltsbyḥ
 wlsạny hạyhtf wyrnm .. yʿln ʿn mjdk)2
 whnrfʿk fy wsṭynạ .. wtfrḥ qlbk ạ̉gẖạnynạ
 sẖfạyfnạ hạtʿtrf bạsmk .. wnqwl bnḥbk</lyrics>
